name: Deeper n' Dipper
description: fight your way to the Dip! the legend tells about the great nacho who found a legendary dip that was protected in deepest trench of time by the evil snacks. no one ever returns from the trench of time.. now, the brave Dipper The Nacho (That’s you!) will be adventuring back to the aztec period in persuit of legendary dip just like the ones who came before. Will he survive?
